descriptionNullable:
### Context

vietnamese news datas were crawled from health category on vnexpress.net site.
All datas are not normalized. 

### Content

`url`: link of the article
`title`: title of the article
`keywords`: keywords of the article
`description`: description of the article
`content`: all contents of the article
`len`: length of the article (words)
`author`: author of the article


### Inspiration

- news title generation
- fake news generation
- sentiment classification
